@host = {{host}}
@token = {{token}}
@documentCollectionId = {{documentCollectionId}}

### Listar enlaces documento ↔ colección (paginado)

GET {{host}}/api/v1/document-collections/{{documentCollectionId}}/documents/
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Con page_size y filtros conocidos (`document_id`, `document_name`, `ordering`)

GET {{host}}/api/v1/document-collections/{{documentCollectionId}}/documents/?page_size=25&ordering=-created_at
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Sin Bearer

GET {{host}}/api/v1/document-collections/{{documentCollectionId}}/documents/
Accept: application/json
